  "title": "Air Hub Baggage Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>You will be responsible for overseeing and executing baggage handling operations across the Control Centre, Departure, Deployment, or Arrival team. Key duties include:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Monitoring and disseminating real-time flight and baggage information.</li>\n  <li>Allocating duties and deploying baggage staff and motorized equipment.</li>\n  <li>Supervising baggage operations at Departure and Arrival racetracks, including timely loading/unloading.</li>\n  <li>Ensuring proper container/trolley setup, baggage documentation, and compliance with security requirements.</li>\n  <li>Handling interline and transfer baggage, including coordination for tight connection flights.</li>\n  <li>Investigating and reporting baggage mishandling or irregularities.</li>\n  <li>Liaising with Load Control, ground handlers, and internal teams for operational updates.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in any discipline</li>\n  <li>Comfortable with shift work</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Clarice Lim (R1656152) | Anchor Search Group Pte Ltd (17C8528)</p>",
